casebody.data:
Telly Lawon NIX, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-1853 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Telly Nix appeals the district court's denial of his application for post-conviction relief, which we construe as a motion to correct an illegal sentence. WRIT ANNULLED.

WRIT ANNULLED.
